                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-police Inspector</hi>). I produce a certificate (<hi rend="italic">Read</hi>:" <hi rend="italic">Central Criminal Court. Alfred Brown, convicted, June</hi>, 1852, <hi rend="italic">on his own confession, of stealing a handkerchief from the person; 
Transported for Seven Years</hi>")—I was present—the prisoner is the person mentioned there.</p>
